snippet.title: Pinball FX3 Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Pinball FX3 is coming to the Nintendo Switch on December 12! Download the game for free and get a free table! 
Exciting unique features on Nintendo Switch including vertical orientation and HD Rumble!
www.pinballfx.com
